# ADMIN — Analizza repo

## Trigger

| Comando | Contesto |
| --- | --- |
| `analizza repo ADMIN-xxx` | Standalone o veve step 2 |
| `veve ADMIN-xxx` | Step 2 |
| Step 0 `procedi` / `gogo` | Gap analysis background |
| `chiudi Story ADMIN-xxx` | Gap test |

**Skill:** `.cursor/skills/jlo-analizza-repo/SKILL.md`

## CLI

```bash
node JiraCORE/jiraCORE.repo..issuekey.gap.analysis.mjs --parent ADMIN-88 --format md
node JiraCORE/jiraCORE.repo..issuekey.gap.analysis.mjs --keys ADMIN-121,ADMIN-122
node JiraCORE/jiraCORE.repo..issuekey.gap.analysis.mjs --parent JLO-507 --format md
```

Key ammesse: `ADMIN-xxx`, `JLO-xxx`.

